gdrive-sync (0.3.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Multiple Google accounts: each with its own remote, local folder,
    schedule, exclusions and conflict handling; account list in the main
    window with add/remove.
  * The first synchronization now runs in the sync daemon: closing the
    setup window asks whether to keep syncing in the background or stop
    and cancel the account setup.
  * v0.2 single-account configurations are migrated automatically.

